Darkness. Light. Chaos. Order. There is a constant battle between these things.  These four simple words, make our world what it is – interesting, adventurous, could be wonderful, could be destructive. It all depends on the path you choose. There is an order of Darkness and an order of Light. There is one hero in our story who choose a different path than anyone else before him. He chose to become evil in the eyes of the world so that he could give the world a chance for Light to bring Order again.  His own, did not accept him, what’s worse, they completely rejected him. He became what they feared the most and what they hated the most. War between the two worlds of Darkness and Light was about to start. The hero fought the ones he created, he assembled. The nation was in turmoil, one part of the nation wanted to kill the hero for what he became, the others wanted to join him. The fight wasn’t between one hero versus the whole nation, the fight was between the nation itself. Those who wanted to join the hero did not have enough courage to actually join him. He became the one left standing. He fought as hard as he could for what he believed in. He used magic, he used strength. Anything and everything, just to keep his dream alive. When he saw that he was about to lose to people he didn’t think where worthy of defeating him or being worthy of anything for that matter, he used the last bit of magic he had, and he changed in to something they wouldn’t recognize. In the confusion the hero escaped the turmoil, in hope to one day come back in to the world he would be accepted in. The ones that wanted to join him, have never seen his new face. They are hiding in the nation, acting like normal people, while they are looking for their hero to help him rise up again and unite them all. In the nation there was still those who were looking for the order of light to bring peace in their world. The order of light had only one member left. The only one who still saw good in the nation, still saw a chance for true peace to rule again. In this world everyone has power, to either help him bring peace to their nation, or to bring chaos in to the nation and the world. His sole purpose has now become to unite them all, in order to defeat the one left standing. The one left standing or the hero, has his own purpose. To come back from the shadows of the darkness he himself created, find his followers, reveal himself to them, and bring his own order in to this broken, forsaken, world.
